column5: I've tried e-mailing them a couple of times and have had no response...I know I could phone them but I'm usually at work or it's too early when I think of it....and they would likely kill me if I did  Maureen
He's likely still catching crap from last time we were up there.
Probably spending time off with the kids...they're off school 'till Monday.
I'd buy Ricks explanations   I tried e-mailing them a couple of months ago Wayne so the holidays is no excuse  maureen
